    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>roughly</strong> <strong>chopped onion </strong>and your <strong>red Thai curry paste</strong> to a <strong>food processor </strong>with your<strong> curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[2 tbsp]<strong> </span>cold water </strong>and blitz into a smooth paste – this is your<strong> khao soi-style curry paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
