    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot </strong>to a small bowl with a squeeze of <strong>lime</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick</strong>-<strong>pickled shallot</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
