    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> medium egg noodles</strong> to a large bowl, cover them with<strong> boiled water </strong>and set aside to soak for 5-6 min and then drain</p><p>Add 1/4 of the <strong>soaked noodles</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 5-6 min or until golden and crispy – these are your <strong>crispy noodles</strong></p>",
