    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken breast </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to brown</p><p>Once the chicken has started to brown, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>and <strong>khao soi-style curry paste</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until fragrant</p>",
