      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained noodles</strong> to a bowl and top with the <strong>coconut chicken breast khao soi</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>quick</strong>-<strong>pickled shallot</strong> and the <strong>crispy noodles</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge </strong>and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>zesty green beans</strong> to the side and enjoy!</p>",
